<L>__{109 (shock cut to sky:}
<A>__{) close on german fighter plane day it screams down vertically, full power, machine guns blazing, then smashes into the earth, shredding to fragments hurled in every direction. the dead german pilot is flung crumpled to the ground. the plane's carcass explodes, filling the screen with fire and black smoke through which we see a brightly colored parachute descending. the figure dangling beneath it passes through the smoke and flames and tumbles to the ground, rolling, his parachute now ablaze. it is cameron dressed in a british flyer's uniform.}
